The Bluetooth Developer App is made to help you developing with bluetooth devices and understanding how they work.
You can:
- Find & see nearby devices
- View manufacturer data and signal strength
- Connect and read out data
- See before connecting if a device is possible an apple or android device
- See what kind of device (TV, headphones, etc) a device is before connecting
- Read out advertisement data
- Pair some devices to your phone
- See information about services and characteristics
- Read out characteristic values and parse them (currently in UTF8 format)
- Read out heartbeat and heartbeat sensor location data
This app does not collect any data about the user.
